ounded by an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll: the inner island would be one ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object, while the surrounding","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"group of disconnected but related buildings.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","type":"topic"}}}